job_description.raw_text: We are seeking a Senior Software Engineer with 5+ years of experience in Python, React, and AWS. The ideal candidate will lead development of scalable web applications, mentor junior developers, and work with cross-functional teams. Requirements include strong problem-solving skills, experience with microservices architecture, and knowledge of CI/CD pipelines.

metadata.original_cv_text:
John Smith
Senior Software Engineer

EXPERIENCE
Software Engineer at TechCorp (2019-2024)
- Developed scalable web applications using Python and Django
- Built responsive frontend interfaces with React and TypeScript
- Implemented CI/CD pipelines using Jenkins and Docker
- Collaborated with cross-functional teams on product development
- Mentored 3 junior developers

SKILLS
- Programming: Python, JavaScript, TypeScript, Java
- Frameworks: Django, React, Node.js, Express
- Cloud: AWS (EC2, S3, Lambda), Docker, Kubernetes
- Databases: PostgreSQL, MongoDB, Redis
- Tools: Git, Jenkins, JIRA, Agile methodologies

EDUCATION
Bachelor of Science in Computer Science
University of Technology (2015-2019)
